# 🔍 Step 2 — Verify channel

Run:

```bash
oc get sub odf-operator -n openshift-storage -o yaml
```

Check:

```yaml
spec:
  channel: ?
```

---

# ❗ If you see:

```yaml
channel: stable-4.19
```

👉 THIS is the problem

---

# ✅ Fix (IMPORTANT)

Patch channel to 4.20:

```bash
oc patch sub odf-operator -n openshift-storage \
--type=merge -p '{"spec":{"channel":"stable-4.20"}}'
```

---

# 🔄 Then watch upgrade

```bash
